cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it introduces a novel prior for Bayesian neural networks. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it discusses the behavior of the proposed prior. Finally, it could be relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it demonstrates the behavior of the prior on real examples.
